step 1: Start
step 2: Initialize variable 
step 3: Define function and error
step 4: Take initial guess (ie x1 and x2)
step 5: Compute fx1 and fx2
step 6: Check for initial guess bracket (ie if fx1 * fx2 < 0) if false goto step 4
step 7: compute for x3 and fx3 (ie x3=(x1+x2)/2 )
step 8: if fx1 * fx3 <0 then x2 = x3 and fx2 = fx3 else x1 = x3 and fx1 = fx3
step 9: display table data
step 10: if |fx3|>error goto step 7
step 11: Stop
